*Margaret* je dala svojim prijateljima najbolje savete. (Margaret gave her friends the best advice.)

Njene ideje su *Margaret* često pomogle da reši stvari. (Her ideas often helped *Margaret* to solve things.)

Život *Margaret* je bio pun izazova. (The life of *Margaret* was full of challenges.)

Ona je uvek bila spremna da pomogne drugima, bilo da se radi o *Margaret* ili nekom drugom. (She was always ready to help others, whether it was *Margaret* or someone else.)